data.description: Discover this like-new gem featuring a custom-built hall tree with bench in the inviting foyer. With a spacious living room bathed in natural light from ample windows, this home offers comfort and style. Enjoy upgraded ceiling fans throughout, enhancing each of the 4 well-sized bedrooms, one perfect for a home office. The master suite is a retreat with an updated walk-in shower. Step outside to the extended patio, ideal for relaxation or entertaining. A blend of modern living and cozy charm. This home is conveniently located just .5 miles to Loop 288 and a short drive to the Denton Water Park.
